TagsString.description:
Custom metadata in the form of key-value pairs.
Must be in the key value format: key1:value;key2:value;

Example:
```json
{
  "key1":"value1",
  "key2":"value2"
}
```

Should be inputted as:
```
?tags=key1:value;key2:value;
```

EngagementSourceString.description:
Custom metadata in the form of a key-value pair.
Must be in the key value format: key:value;

Example:
```json
{
  "key":"value"
}
```

Should be input as:
```
?source=key:val;
```
